{"tid":1631382,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"請集中火力！已經沒有後路！團結一致！ 請入場！","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T21:15:18.000Z","uid":187007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"92cf1174de99111ea15fb994935d3903389a279c","tid":1631382,"uid":187007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dJJVE4V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdJJVE4V.png&h=e8d8a4f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NoxbXRB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNoxbXRB.png&h=3ca3a3f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先提今日有瘋狂的士加速撞上行人路，兩人受傷，其中<br />\n<br />\n一人雙腳骨折。<br />\n<br />\n第二單 初中女童被捕，神情慌張。<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多濫捕不公，妨礙記者拍攝等等 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講番小弟玩隻新game先<br />\n<br />\n比人恰到傻，球証球員咩鳩都係佢地d人<br />\n<br />\n慘在仲要自己人都仲未齊心未夠決心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再咁落去都唔知要傷要死幾多人，有時有d又叫分區<br />\n<br />\n又分前線和理非咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都比人恰到上心口仲要就住<br />\n<br />\n就住？要贏我睇就有兩個方法 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正式全面開戰 而家根本無可能零成本贏 必需要有所<br />\n<br />\n犧牲，（注：我地已經犧牲左失去左好多）<br />\n<br />\n60歲阿伯阿婆都行出黎支持 ，諗唔到有咩籍口唔出<br />\n<br />\n黎對抗。 <br />\n<br />\n200萬精兵齊罩一人一舊磚拎係手企硬！！！<br />\n<br />\n當日定下時間要求對家正面回應加立刻下台 ，否則<br />\n<br />\n全面抗爭到底！<br />\n<br />\n第二方案 全面性/強制性罷工 等對家去盡 逼到緊急<br />\n<br />\n狀態 ，慢慢溫水煮蛙，最後只會輸。<br />\n<br />\n由第一日有烈士 到今日太子死人 不斷有發現屍體 <br />\n<br />\n由催淚彈2015 70幾粒 ，到2019年 幾千粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到真槍實彈 變到常態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再係咁落去捉都捉得7788 都無人再敢出黎。<br />\n<br />\n暫時抗爭遊行，開花等等都沖擊唔到核心。<br />\n<br />\n要錫春袋必需要令到敵人有所顧忌，一面罷，一面<br />\n<br />\n勇，一面罷雙管齊下！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gqfg89F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGqfg89F.jpg&h=be6c7994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">本人嚴正守法唔鼓勵人犯法。</span><br />\n<br />\n以上為打機攻略完！！ 光復香港，時代革命！！！ <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人反抗！！！要有行動！！！<br />\n</span><br />\n叫口號敵人唔會怕！要錫春袋！！！"},{"pid":"bf3063fc5e0958b29504ea6e4e17ac73a3885659","tid":1631382,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:25:08.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ac1d6db0ca7e26a4e7a202821c1ba067eed0d379","tid":1631382,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:35.000Z","msg":"仲要有左膠 阻撚住哂 屌 去死啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「極重要」《三份英國外交及國會報告》：當代及後世香港抗爭者之啟示</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631132</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"414176096e2c5fbf4e6dcfe2012a1b08f5826a25","tid":1631382,"uid":187007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac1d6db0ca7e26a4e7a202821c1ba067eed0d379","tid":1631382,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:35.000Z","msg":"仲要有左膠 阻撚住哂 屌 去死啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「極重要」《三份英國外交及國會報告》：當代及後世香港抗爭者之啟示</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631132</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"左膠必需制裁，但太重手出事都會有反效果<br />\n<br />\n正確做法，先神獸但唔好太重手，再影底佢身份証<br />\n<br />\n方便起底。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68759da1825fed7cfcf391fb47ace28504860da4","tid":1631382,"uid":187007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:15:18.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"}]}